          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measured the gamma-spectra from",
                " Al-27(gamma,xgamma')Mg-26 and",
                " Al-27(gamma,ngamma')Al-26 reactions induced by",
                " bremsstrahlung gamma-quanta with 32-MeV end-point",
                " energy. The detection angle was 140 degrees.",
                " Integral cross sections of photonucleon",
                " reactions on Al-27 with formation of final nuclei",
                " in separate states are determined.",
                "The results are interpreted making use of the state",
                " population data from one-nucleon-transfer reactions.",
                "Conclusions are derived concerning the mechanism of",
                " photonucleon reactions and the part of isospin in",
                " the formation and decay the giant resonance of the",
                " Al-27 nucleus and of some other 1d2S-shell nuclei."
              ]
            }
          ],
